{"tid":1809107,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢爆疫症】商戶指患者集中市場西區 一齊打牌都感染","createTime":"2020-01-03T00:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T02:18:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e15ac897a0206127e0bb14c3daab1e639f329b22","tid":1809107,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:35:01.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢爆發多宗不明原因肺炎，作為病毒傳播源頭的武漢華南海鮮市場，昨日起被責令休市。然而，病毒似乎早已在市場附近地區肆虐。內地媒體今日報道指，有涉事市場的商戶稱，街市內的西區十街、二街、四街均有人罹患肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n華南海鮮市場位於江漢區，據商家稱，市場內東、西兩個區域共有28條街，共計有650多個檔位，從業人員超過1,500人。報道指，該海鮮市場位於一棟建築的一樓，攤檔擁擠，走廊只容兩人並排行走。由於該處商家主要出售海鮮，因此地面潮濕，而商家在處理海鮮時，不時會有水濺到地面。<br />\n<br />\n一名女商販表示，其熟悉的一名患者起初並未注意到病情的嚴重性，「一涼一熱，就咳嗽，咳嗽後有點低燒，前後拖了10天才去醫院，後來有點嚴重，打針已不奏效。」另有兩名商販表示，西區一商家及其家人均被感染。此外，市場內有幾名商販平時聚在一起打牌，此次也被感染。<br />\n<br />\n上月31日（本周二）下午，內媒記者在武漢市中心醫院探訪時，有兩名患者家屬都表示，看到了「華南」的病人被送到了隔離病房。在隔離病房門外，可以看到有安保人員和醫務人員執勤，不允許閒雜人員進入。有商販稱：「他們去醫院看家屬的時候，患病家屬穿的是標有『華南』字樣的病服。」<br />\n<br />\n報道並指，記者周二在現場發現，該市場有疑似售賣野味的情況。一名買家來到市場深處一商戶，明確提出要買兔子和野雞，對方起初稱自己只賣家禽，但遲疑一會後，又指着店角籠子裏的兔子稱，這是「自己吃的」。旁邊一名正整理貨物的女商販多次觀察買家後說，「兔子有殺好的」，並報價18元人民幣（下同，約20港元）一斤。最終，雙方以50元（約56港元）的價格成交。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200102/large/1577962215_f639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200102%2Flarge%2F1577962215_f639.jpg&h=7905b393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200102/60443784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60443784&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7H%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=fa41e7ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60443784&h=5c5c2d47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200102/60443784</a>"},{"pid":"5261cddb78daec83fc80f659f24a9bbf235d0839","tid":1809107,"uid":182624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"又係野味，到底佢哋有幾熱愛食野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bada109a001d920ab3f837f6ddc596099b9c01bd","tid":1809107,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:52:18.000Z","msg":"講到野味，印象中沙士都係因為野味？"},{"pid":"59dd3f3bcafe6ef32bf0145cc37d37c1389efcf7","tid":1809107,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99784d8ac9c3eba7f1c3f165dee8e54178cd2085","tid":1809107,"uid":78662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53c8dcbf251fb451c4f1cf6891d7fbb573b98c8","tid":1809107,"uid":219564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:14:16.000Z","msg":"屌真係生番嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c447c0ef886e05049c6a33e874e511a2b50695d","tid":1809107,"uid":173060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bada109a001d920ab3f837f6ddc596099b9c01bd","tid":1809107,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:52:18.000Z","msg":"講到野味，印象中沙士都係因為野味？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:14:42.000Z","msg":"果子狸"},{"pid":"325194058bb37e278823440d2a9c88993b57b333","tid":1809107,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:33:52.000Z","msg":"兔兔很可愛<br />\n你不能吃牠"},{"pid":"41083a8d0edbc3d06e649b147f6ea5ba34620046","tid":1809107,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5261cddb78daec83fc80f659f2